abstract: Sergiy Stakhovsky defeats Stan Wawrinka in quarterfinals of Open 13 tennis tournament in France; other tennis news noted.
lead_paragraph: Wawrinka was knocked out of the Open 13 by Sergiy Stakhovsky of Ukraine with a 6-4, 3-6, 6-4 loss in the quarterfinals Friday.

headline.main: Stan Wawrinka Is Eliminated in Marseille
